The extra two queries line up with workflow-state recalculation inside `AdminPaidBookingSerializer`: the admin queue view prefetches payments and partner profile edges, but not the passport/document relations that `sync_booking_state()` touches during serialization. I’m tightening that queryset now so the admin review page stays within the intended bounded query budget.
