I’ve isolated the two wasted queries. One is the extra filtered `SUM()` on the admin queue, which can be folded into the existing summary aggregate. The other is `sync_booking_state()` eagerly touching operator-document state even for bookings that are still in traveller/payment-review stages. I’m tightening both paths together so the fix preserves response shape instead of weakening the test.
