| SEC-B3 | Next | `SEC-010`, `DS-P1-002` | Remove cross-tenant re-binding from partner booking mutations | Use the already-authenticated partner context for booking actions, ignore request-supplied `partner_session_token` selectors, and add regression coverage for cross-tenant tampering attempts. |
| SEC-B4 | Next | `SEC-004`, `DS-P1-006` | Add exposure guardrails and verification | Add management/security regression tests, assert serializers never emit auth/device tokens on public or cross-role surfaces, and confirm media/docs flags stay disabled in production unless intentionally enabled. |

